description:
Thomas Middleditch (Silicon Valley) joins Anna and Sim this week to talk about Hollywood egos, spring cleaning, alternate careers and Anna pitches him a new app idea! Later, they call Kellie, whose family is having problems with her leaving the Mormon church with her husband, and Katie, whose friend is getting too involved with her dating life.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
